{"lastModified":1771338717406,"uri":"c::29886948373::vessel::8dd00d80-f2cb-11ef-bf0e-4bee349e1670","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nElegant & Spacious Yacht Interior\nFashion Cantiere Navale 72ft is an excellent choice for those who wish to experience a unique sailing adventure. This yacht is equipped with three beautifully designed cabins, each with a private bathroom for maximum privacy and relaxation. The master and VIP cabins are furnished with king-size beds, while the twin cabin offers a comfortable double bed. All this makes Fashion Cantiere Navale 72 an ideal choice for families, couples, or groups of friends.\n\nPremium Amenities & Modern Comforts\nEquipped with cutting edge technologies and opulent features, the Fashion Cantiere Navale 72ft guarantees a  seamless and luxurious charter experience. From its spacious lounge areas to its sophisticated exterior, every detail is designed for your enjoyment and relaxation at sea.\n\nProfessional Crew for a Personalized Charter Experience\nSteadfast dedication of our captains and our stewardess’ attentiveness, makes this private yacht charter an exceptional experience, ensuring every journey is smooth and tailored to your preferences. Do you want to island-hop, explore hidden bays, or perhaps enjoy fine dining on board? Our crew is at your service at any moment.\n\nSail the Adriatic in Style\nUncover the beauties of Croatia’s spectacular islands and explore coastal towns’ rich history aboard this luxury yacht charter. Whether you want to stroll through the streets of old town Dubrovnik or discover the vibrant nightlife of Hvar, the Fashion Cantiere Navale 72ft is your ticket to an unforgettable yachting adventure.","blueprint":{"name":"F72","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::8dd00d80-f2cb-11ef-bf0e-4bee349e1670::assets::63193de0-f2d1-11ef-96f8-3b50d7b486a7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::8dd00d80-f2cb-11ef-bf0e-4bee349e1670::assets::6318a1a0-f2d1-11ef-96f7-3b